<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会<delay20 />开始了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要一起来数今天放的烟花数量吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，小心别像属羊一样数睡着咯。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花<delay8 />真漂亮<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然总会被这超响的声音吓到，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但也正因为有这样的气势才更打动人心！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
装点夜空的升空烟花，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有和人很相似的地方呢，你不觉得吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论是颜色还是形状，<delay8 />
每一发烟花都有独一无二的个性，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就是魅力啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你拍照了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是让人忍不住想要
用照片记录下来的美景呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是实际看到的烟花
要更漂亮一些！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论什么时候，<delay8 />
美丽的烟花都会让人着迷～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />求婚的时候，
用100发升空烟花来代替100朵玫瑰，<delay8 />
我也会非常高兴呢！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />大家都看烟花看得入迷了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能看到大家开心的笑脸，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很高兴！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么了，<delay20 />我的脸上沾了什么东西吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你为什么突然这样盯着我看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay20 />你说我的眼睛里倒映着烟花？<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />就算我看着比平时更漂亮了，<delay8 />
你也别一直盯着看呀！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我会害羞的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />已经快结束了啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快乐的时光总是这么短暂呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然内心非常不舍，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但还是好好享受这最后的美景吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">还能欢喜地欣赏这美丽烟花的时间，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已经不多了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终究要迎来结束的时刻，<delay8 />真让人伤心。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才的烟花也好美啊～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一不小心就忘记了年龄，玩开了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎？<delay20 />你问我几岁了？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不可以随便问女生的年龄哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>